• uuid

        • string

        Description

        The UUID type contains an UUID encoded as a string. The used format is the 8-4-4-4-12 format.

        Example: 78c5fbbf-12ac-40c0-ab50-a1a776e0e259

      • timestamp

        • string

        Description

        The timestamp type contains a date and time encoded using the ISO-8601 format.

        Example: 2013-03-14T15:15:35.450Z
